.Dd February 19, 2002
.Dt HILINFO 1 HP300
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm hilinfo
.Nd provides information on HIL devices
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm hilinfo
.Op Fl a
.Op Fl t
.Ar device ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
prints information about the
.Ar device
list.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl a
For each
.Ar device ,
display the type and the complete hil information bitstring.
.It Fl t
For each
.Ar device ,
display the type.
.El
.Pp
If no options are given, the type will be printed (that is,
.Nm
will behave as if
.Fl t
had been passed).
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr hil 4
.Sh HISTORY
A
.Nm
command appeared in
.Bx 4.4 .
